
  esplor kiosk - WPE WebKit on Wayland/DRM

  Browser (cogctl --system help for full list)
    cogctl --system reload          reload current page
    cogctl --system open <url>      navigate to new URL
    cogctl --system ping            check whether cog is running
    systemctl restart cog           full browser restart
    journalctl -u cog -f            follow browser log

  Display
    display on                      wake display (CEC + DDC/CI)
    display standby                 low-power standby
    display off                     full soft-off
    display status                  show current DDC power mode

  System
    systemctl list-timers           active timers (cog-watchdog, etc.)
    journalctl -k --since -5min     recent kernel messages
    top -b -n 1 | head -n 6         quick resource snapshot

